  <div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
    <h1 class="mb-4">Universiti Tun Hussein Onn Malaysia (UTHM)</h1>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>
          UTHM is a public technical university located in Batu Pahat, Johor. It focuses mainly on engineering, technology, and applied sciences.
        </p>

        <h4>Overview</h4>
        <p>
          Established in 1993, UTHM has grown to become a respected institution for technical education in Malaysia. The university offers undergraduate, postgraduate, and research programs across multiple faculties.
        </p>

        <h4>Faculties & Programs</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Faculty of Engineering Technology</li>
          <li>Faculty of Electrical and Electronic Engineering</li>
          <li>Faculty of Civil and Environmental Engineering</li>
          <li>Faculty of Computer Science and Information Technology</li>
          <li>Faculty of Science</li>
          <!-- Add more faculties as needed -->
        </ul>

        <h4>Admission & Application</h4>
        <p>
          For admission requirements, application deadlines, and scholarship opportunities, please visit the official UTHM admissions page.
        </p>
